name: FLEXNET
overview:
FLEXNET is desktop virtualization software and hardware solutions reseller in the United States. The company provides desktop virtualization kits that enable users to share Web browsers, instant messaging, e-mail, office suites, and multimedia application for users who manage schools, training rooms, libraries, and office applications. In addition, it offers business solutions, such as general office, manufacturing, and healthcare solutions; education solutions, including K-12 education and higher education solutions; and government and non-profit/NGO solutions.

The company was founded in 2007 and is based in Jackson, MS.
